channel.title: Compiler error plz help!
channel.description:
I was adding ints for some custom items on my pi and compiled and got 1 error this was the error
[code=java]ItemDef.java:184: orphaned case case 15000: ^ 1 error Press any key to continue . . .[/code]
heres my itemdef http://pastebin.com/47Rhb1wE there error is online 184 i guess an orpahned case whatever that means.... i read up on it but still am confused help please!

item.title: Compiler error plz help!
item.dc:creator: @xx_extremez_xx xx extremez xx
item.description:
@xx_extremez_xx wrote:

[quote=“Rash, post:4, topic:385103”][quote author=xx extremez xx link=topic=480869.msg3520929#msg3520929 date=1299393574]

you did something like
break;
}
which has moved a case outside of the switchstatement.

remove the }.

i cant find the }
[/quote]

Find the case you added recently, and check to see if it has

break;
}

If not, check if you added the case OUTSIDE of a switchstatement, in which case it needs to be added.[/quote]
ya theres no } i think i added the case outside of a switchstatement were can i find a switchstatement?
